# Creating this file DISABLES Stow's built-in default ignore list,
# so the GNU Stow 2.4.1 defaults are reproduced verbatim below,
# then extended with project-only files that must never be stowed.

# --- GNU Stow default ignore list (preserved) ---
RCS
.+,v

CVS
\.\#.+
\.cvsignore

\.svn
_darcs
\.git
\.gitignore

.+~
\#.*\#

^/README.*
^/LICENSE.*
^/COPYING

# --- Project-only context: dotfiles repo CLAUDE.md must stay local ---
# Needed as project memory when cwd=~/dotfiles, but must NOT be stowed to
# ~/CLAUDE.md (would leak dotfiles/Stow context into every $HOME-rooted session).
^/CLAUDE.md
